node.text:
What race would @alex_bowman prefer to win? The #DAYTONA500 of course.

Get to know the No. 48 driver better before he climbs behind the wheel of the @allyracing Chevy @daytona!

node.title: This or That with Alex Bowman

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 11, 2021 tagging @kylelarsonracin, and @valvoline. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text:
The last two times we took on new tracks (@nashvillesuperspeedway and @nascaratcota), our days ended in victory lane. 🏁

Tune in to NBC on Sunday at 1 p.m. ET as we take on the @indianapolismotorspeedway road course and look to make history at another new track!

node.text:
They’re back. 🔥

@chaseelliott9 will be sporting his iconic @hooters colors this weekend at the @indianapolismotorspeedway road course — tune in to NBC on Sunday at 1 p.m. ET!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 09, 2021 tagging @hendrickautomotivegroup. May be an image of one or more people, car and outdoors.

node.text: @kylelarsonracin's momentous day @wgi1948 secured road course win No. 24 for Hendrick Motorsports, most of all teams! 🏆

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 09, 2021 tagging @kylelarsonracin, and @hendrickautomotivegroup. May be an image of 1 person and text.

node.text: A 1-2 finish + a trip to victory lane = a fun day @wgi1948! 👊

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 09, 2021 tagging @kylelarsonracin, and @hendrickautomotivegroup. May be an image of 1 person and text.
Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 09, 2021 tagging @chaseelliott9, @williambyron, @axaltaracing, and @napaknowhow. May be an image of 2 people and text.

node.text:
Back to their winning ways! 🙌 

@kylelarsonracin and the HendrickCars.com team have won four of the last nine races of 2021. 🏁🏁🏁🏁

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hendrick Motorsports on August 08, 2021.

node.text: After securing his second road course victory so far this year, @kylelarsonracin becomes the fifth driver to win for Hendrick Motorsports @wgi1948! 🏆

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 08, 2021 tagging @hendrickautomotivegroup. May be an image of 2 people and text.

node.text:
Win No. 5️⃣ for the No. 5️⃣ .

@kylelarsonracin captures the win @wgi1948 in the HendrickCars.com Chevy! 🏁

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 08, 2021 tagging @alex_bowman, @chaseelliott9, @napaknowhow, and @allyracing. May be an image of 2 people and people standing.

node.text:
Time to take on the road course action. 💪

Tune in to NBCSN now — the excitement @wgi1948 is about to begin!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hendrick Motorsports on August 08, 2021. May be an image of car, road and text.

node.text: It's road course race day @wgi1948, and we are revved up. 😎

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 07, 2021 tagging @allyracing. May be an image of car, road and text that says 'WATKINS GLEN INTERNATIONAL SUNDAY, AUGUST 8 3 PM PMET ET YNBCS BOWMARI'.

node.text: It's almost time for the ⬅️ and ➡️ turns of @wgi1948!
